<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>{{statusCode}} — Gabriel Maciel</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/assets/css/screen.css">
</head>
<body>

<nav class="sans" style="position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 99; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95); backdrop-filter: blur(14px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(14px); border-bottom: 1px solid #DDE4E8; padding: 0 24px; height: 64px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;">
    <a href="/" class="serif" style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: #0C2D3E; text-decoration: none;">GM</a>
    <div style="display: flex; gap: 28px; align-items: center;">
        <a href="/posts/" style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #0C2D3E; text-decoration: none;">Artigos</a>
        <a href="/projetos/" style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; color: #0C2D3E; text-decoration: none;">Projetos</a>
        <a href="/#contato" class="btn-gold" style="padding: 9px 20px; font-size: 13px; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block;">Fale comigo</a>
    </div>
</nav>

<section style="background: #0C2D3E; min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 80px 32px; position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
    <div style="position: absolute; inset: 0; opacity: 0.04; background-image: radial-gradient(circle, #fff 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 24px 24px; pointer-events: none;"></div>
    <div style="max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; position: relative;">
        <div class="serif" style="font-size: 120px; font-weight: 700; color: rgba(212,169,32,0.15); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: -20px;">{{statusCode}}</div>
        <div style="width: 44px; height: 3px; background: #D4A920; border-radius: 2px; margin: 0 auto 20px;"></div>
        <h1 class="serif" style="font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 42px); font-weight: 700; color: #FFFFFF; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.15;">
            {{#if errorMessage}}{{errorMessage}}{{else}}Página não encontrada{{/if}}
        </h1>
        <p class="sans" style="font-size: 16px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 36px;">
            A página que você procura não existe ou foi movida. Tente voltar para o início.
        </p>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
            <a href="/" class="btn-gold" style="text-decoration: none;">Voltar para o início</a>
            <a href="/posts/" class="btn-outline" style="text-decoration: none;">Ver artigos</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

</body>
</html>
